  "text": "The Amount brain denotes the brain radioactivity at time t; the R t 0 C p \u00f0 \u00ded is plasma AUC from the time of injection; and C p \u00f0t\u00de is instantaneous plasma activity at time \u00bc t. Plasma concentrations were simulated using equation [CITATION_1] , and predicted primary plasma PK parameters. The",
